The case is currently under further investigation.
The relevant person in charge of the Guangdong Maritime Police Bureau said that it will continue to maintain a high-pressure situation in the future, crack down on various illegal and criminal activities of smuggling at sea, and maintain good order in the waters under its jurisdiction.
