Xinhua News Agency, Nanchang, July 26 (Guo Dongming, Xiong Liang) The Recruitment Office of the Jiangxi Provincial People's Government recently made it clear that individuals or their children who have excelled in this flood relief and disaster relief mission meet the conditions for recruitment, and those who are qualified in both medical examinations and political examinations will be given priority.
"After the young conscripts are registered, we will jointly check with the communities where the young conscripts live, the Street Armed Forces Department and the Fuyang District Recruitment Office to give priority to the soldiers."
