Xinhua News Agency, Dalian, July 25 (Reporters Cai Xinjun and Cui Shihao) Dalian City released news on the 25th. From 15: 00 on July 24 to 14: 00 on July 25, there were no new local confirmed cases of new coronary pneumonia in Dalian, 24 new cases of asymptomatic infection, and no new suspected cases.
