After research and judgment, Dalian City decided to strengthen strict control over close contacts of all employees of Dalian Kaiyang World Seafood Co., Ltd. and close contacts of close contacts, and implement centralized isolation medical observation on the 14th and at least 2 nucleic acid tests.
