Xinhua News Agency, Beijing, July 25, People's Daily, July 26, commentator's article: Concentrate on doing your own affairs and building new advantages for future development
At present, the global epidemic and the world economic situation are still severe and complex, and the challenges facing my country's development are unprecedented.
Maintaining strategic determination, enhancing confidence in victory, and concentrating our efforts on our own affairs are the keys to our response to various risks and challenges.
At the recent entrepreneur symposium, General Secretary Xi Jinping emphasized that in the current external environment of rising protectionism, downturn in the world economy, and shrinking global markets, we must concentrate our efforts on our own affairs, give full play to the advantages of the domestic super-large-scale market, and gradually form a new development pattern that takes the domestic big cycle as the main body and the domestic and international double cycles promote each other, improve the modernization level of the industrial chain supply chain, vigorously promote scientific and technological innovation, accelerate key core technologies, and create new advantages for future development.
Those who observe the situation are wise, and those who control the situation win.
In the external environment of the in-depth development of economic globalization, the "two ends" of markets and resources have played an important role in the rapid development of my country.
Now, the world under the impact of the epidemic is undergoing profound changes, facing more unstable and uncertain factors, and economic globalization is encountering headwinds and turning waves.
To be prepared for a longer period of time to respond to changes in the external environment, and to promote my country's economy to ride the wind and waves and achieve stability and long-term development, an extremely important aspect is to take the expansion and satisfaction of domestic demand as the strategic basis for development, give full play to its own advantages, and add impetus to my country's economic development through the prosperity of the domestic economy and the smooth flow of the domestic cycle, and drive the recovery of the world economy.
We must deeply realize that building a complete domestic demand system is related to my country's long-term development and long-term stability.
The Party Central Committee reviewed the situation and clearly proposed to resolutely implement the strategy of expanding domestic demand. This is the need to respond to the impact of the epidemic, to maintain the long-term sustainable and healthy development of my country's economy, and to meet the needs of the people's growing good life.
The advantage of a large economy is that it is internally recyclable.
