However, in March, April, and May, the market turnover increased by 78%, 199%, and 35% respectively; the number of orders increased by 141%, 152%, and 50% respectively; and the number of receptions increased by 81%, 112%, and 28% respectively.
The "Report" points out that the development of the shared accommodation industry has been promising for a long time, but there are still many uncertainties in the near future.
